\nw[Receptionist]The ritual of childbirth is a ceremony to grow a
pregnant fetus and give birth. It is recommended
because it has a low mortality rate and imposes
less burden on the mother.

\nw[Receptionist]By infusing magic power into the fetus, we promote
its growth. Please understand that in order to do
so, the act of injecting semen into the uterus
needs to be performed multiple times.

\nw[Receptionist]The period will take about a week. If you have any
business such as going on a dispatched quest, it
cannot be done. If you are from your mercenary
group, I will accept it anytime since you receive
money from Prae-san.

time. However, it cannot be done unless the belly
has grown enough.

\nw[\N[21]]Fross, let me thank you again. Thank you for
treating me.

\nw[Fross]You're welcome. I received the payment from Prae-
san, so you don't have to worry about it.

\nw[Fross]It's true that I was injured, but thanks to Prae-
san's magic, my life-threatening condition has
been resolved.

\nw[\N[21]]Indeed... I never expected to survive that
injury...
\nw[\N[21]]Ah, all three of you are okay.

\nw[Fross]If anything happens, please let me know right
away.
\nw[Fross]Please come for a check-up after you're called.
\nw[Fross]Hello, you seem to be doing well.

\nw[Fross]Yes, I work here during the day, so when you go
outside the town, I'll accompany you.

\nw[Fross]Yes, I'm doing well. Please take care too, \N[21]-
san.

\nw[Fross]Even if you're constantly on edge, you'll end up
getting tired. Don't forget to take breaks, okay?

\nw[Fross]I'll be finishing repaying my debt soon, but since
I've become Prae-san's attending physician, it
seems like I'll be going to the infirmary often.
\nw[\N[21]]Can I talk to you for a moment?

\nw[\N[21]]Ah, that's right... You said you would become mine
in the carriage, didn't you?

\nw[\N[21]]So, it's okay for Fross to listen to what I say,
right?

\nw[Fross]If it's about that matter, I'm sorry, but please
don't take it seriously.

\nw[Fross]Please just ignore the words spoken during sexual
activity. Most of the time, reason goes out the
window.

\nw[Fross]I've seen various things, including sexual magic,
so even though my reason goes out the window, it
doesn't mean I'm speaking from the heart.

\nw[Fross]My judgment deteriorates. That's why I become
easily influenced by others. Therefore, I have
made a decision not to keep promises made during
sexual activity.

\nw[Fross]Even if what I say doesn't reflect my true
feelings, I often find myself nodding in
agreement. And even if I try to be careful, my
reason goes out the window, so I can't handle it.

\nw[\N[21]]Um, in that case, what about what happened back
then...
\nw[Fross]I'm sorry if you ended up believing it.

\nw[Fross]However, I would be happy if you could treat me as
an equal companion and get along with me.

\nw[\N[21]]Ah, ah, yeah... From now on, please take care of
me.
\nw[Fross]Yes, please feel free to call on me anytime.

\nw[\N[21]]Well, I guess it's not that easy to win her
over...

\nw[Fross]Please discuss the promise in a situation where we
can have a proper conversation.

\nw[Fross]I'm in the middle of work, so please postpone your
business for later.

\nw[\N[21]]Did Fross-sensei examine Prae? Did she provide
more detailed examination results at that time?

\nw[Fross]Even if you say in detail, I didn't really
understand. Because the body structure is
different, there's nothing I can do about it.

\nw[Fross]Well, since we're all living beings, there are
some similarities, but Prae-san has too many
different parts.

\nw[Fross]What I understood is that her internal organs are
missing and she experiences discomfort when using
magic.

\nw[Fross]Sensei is a renowned doctor. Even so, I couldn't
understand, so it's difficult to go any further.

\nw[Fross]Since I regularly measure her pulse and body
temperature, if she seems unwell, I will make her
rest.

\nw[Fross]Since Prae-san is not a species with a body
temperature that fluctuates like a powerful fire
magic user, I should be able to assess her
condition based on that.

\nw[\N[21]]I understand. If there's anything I can help with,
please let me know.
\nw[Fross]\N[21]-san, please take care of your health as well.
\nw[Fross]Please talk to me after work, okay?
\nw[\N[21]]What did Fross think of the Longe City Dungeon?

\nw[Fross]That was dangerous. It seems like many people
would get addicted to it.

\nw[Fross]Being violated inside that dungeon feels really
good. You can't experience that pleasure easily.

\nw[Fross]I would be happy if they introduced it nearby. I
feel like I could go there every day.
\nw[Fross]Sex is enjoyable and feels good, you know.
\nw[Fross]It would be nice if \N[21]-san could also enjoy it.
\nw[Fross]Please try not to talk about explicit things here.
\nw[Fross]Please save the conversation for after work, okay?

\nw[Fross]It's about the healer. As you know, we weren't
able to heal Prae this time.

\nw[Fross]Treating injuries and illnesses is basically just
following past cases and treatment methods.

\nw[Fross]So, there are no established treatment methods for
unprecedented injuries or illnesses. Therefore, we
have to conduct new research...

\nw[Fross]There are no facilities in this town where we can
conduct research. We also have to treat people, so
we don't have time for research.

\nw[Fross]Becoming a researcher would take away time for
treating people's ailments, and it goes against my
purpose.

\nw[Fross]I was thinking if there was any way to figure it
out... but it's still difficult, isn't it?

\nw[\N[21]]Did you ask any researchers about this incident?
Or did you not learn the healing method from
Ginny?

\nw[Fross]Regarding the treatment method this time, it
required a large amount of magic power and also
required the same type of magic power. Even if I
were taught, it was impossible for me to control
my magic power.

\nw[\N[21]]If you knew how to control magic power, could you
have done it?

\nw[Fross]I don't have enough magical power. Ginny-san has a
much greater magical power compared to me as a
healer, and her magical control is amazing.

\nw[Fross]I'm already past my growth period, and my magical
power doesn't increase quickly. It would be
difficult for me to learn that magic while I'm
still alive.

\nw[\N[21]]\N[1], \N[3], and I were greatly helped by Fross.
While Prae was the one who revived us, it's thanks
to Fross that we can still move around in good
health like this.

\nw[\N[21]]There may be people who can't be helped by Fross,
but as someone who was helped, I am grateful to
Fross.

\nw[\N[21]]So have confidence. There are many people who have
been helped by Fross, you know.

\nw[Fross]Thank you very much. Indeed, it is not a time to
lose confidence.

\nw[Fross]There are many people who get injured or become
sick, you know. First, we need to properly fulfill
our current duties in front of us.

\nw[Fross]It's important to have the right person for the
right job. No one can do everything alone, so I
also need to do my best with what I can do.
\nw[Fross]Please save the conversation for after work, okay?

\nw[\N[21]]The woman I was with before... Her name was Finis,

\nw[Fross]Even if you ask me that, I'm not sure... but she

\nw[\N[21]]Is that so... It's true that she seemed to lack

\nw[Fross]Thank you very much for helping Rodrigo-san. You

\nw[\N[21]](I guess being weak is no good... I'll end up

\nw[\N[21]](I guess individual strength is important after

\nw[\N[21]](The others have already gone home, so I guess

\nw[Fross]How about it...? Do you understand anything?

\nw[Prae]Hmm, it seems you're quite weakened... but I'll

\nw[Fross]Since you don't have any injuries, I was wondering

\nw[Prae]Hmm, it seems your condition has improved a bit.

\nw[Prae]Is there no magician who can investigate?

\nw[Fross]If it's something simple, I should be able to

\nw[\N[21]]No, he came yesterday, so he probably won't come

\nw[Prae]Sayoka. If it were you, I could entrust you with

\nw[Prae]Before that, Fross. This will be a different

\nw[Fross]That... I'm sorry, but I definitely don't have

\nw[Fross]A-Afterwards, I'll figure something out... Could

\nw[Prae]We're not strangers, so it's fine. But please

elsewhere to pay it off.

\nw[Prae]Well, in that case, should we try symptomatic

\nw[Prae]If that's the case, we should be able to restore

\nw[Prae]It would be best to ask \N[1] or \N[3], wouldn't

\nw[Prae]What's wrong, \N[21]? If you have something to say,

\nw[Prae]The best way to obtain magical power is through

\nw[Prae]I don't know the exact amount of magical power we

\nw[Fross]If it's possible, I would like to ask for a favor.

\nw[Prae]Fross is a follower of the Amor religion. And she

\nw[Prae]If there is a doctor more skilled than myself to

\nw[\N[21]]Eh... Ah, well, I guess you're right.

\nw[Prae]You're just rejecting it reflexively, aren't you?
You should think a little more before speaking.

\nw[\N[21]](I was just thinking until a moment ago that I

method...)

\nw[\N[21]](...If it means repaying Prae's favor, then I

\nw[Fross]Um... You two are lovers, right...? But since you

\nw[Fross]So... I thought that's what you wanted, but is

\nw[\N[21]](Even though I tried not to think about it... when

\nw[\N[21]](...No, I'm getting excited...! Even though this

\nw[Prae]\N[21], I will let you make the decision this time.

\nw[Prae]I won't allow that. You will decide.

\nw[\N[21]](I remember Louis telling me to break down my

\nw[\N[21]](Even though you say that, it feels like this is

\nw[\N[21]](I'll be the one to report to them... If they

\nw[\N[21]](They're probably both in the storage room...)

\nw[\N[21]]Isn't there a part that can't be helped? After
